>> 0xFF ¶

>> "--- Booleans ---" ¶

>> #1 ¶
>> #0 ¶
cmp_gt = (᱑᱒ > ᱔)
cmp_lt = (᱔ > ᱑᱒)
>> cmp_gt ¶
>> cmp_lt ¶
>> #᱑ ¶
